<div id="pf43d4" class="pf w4f h303" data-page-no="43d4"><div class="pc pc43d4 w4f h303"><div class="t m632 xa1 h49 y2f55 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 4 April 22-28 </div><div class="t m27c x16 h49 y23c9 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The dragon was wroth with the </div><div class="t m5c7 x92 h49 y1627 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">woman, and went to make war with </div><div class="t mb63 x92 h49 yf75 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the remnant of her seed, which keep </div><div class="t m1631 x92 h49 y4da ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the commandments of God, and have </div><div class="t mdbb x92 h49 y125e ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the testimony of Jesus Christ&quot; </div><div class="t m775 x92 h49 y1493 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 12:17). </div><div class="t m61c x16 h35 y81a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Throughout the centuries Satan has </div><div class="t m4aa x92 h35 y7a7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">used various political and religious or </div><div class="t m983 x92 h35 y4fb ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritual powers with two purposes: </div><div class="t ma7a x92 h35 y3cc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(1) to corrupt the faith, and (2) to </div><div class="t m882 x92 h35 y97a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">coerce the conscience. </div><div class="t mf27 x71 h35 ycea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">During the early centuries of the </div><div class="t m2ce x92 h35 y29b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christian era, through the Roman </div><div class="t m826 x92 h35 y53d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Empire, the enemy&apos;s method was </div><div class="t m2e1 x92 h35 y77a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">persecution, intimidation, and death. </div><div class="t m3ec x92 h35 y76b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">But in spite of this the church </div><div class="t m8ff x92 h35 y597 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">continued to grow, and Jesus was </div><div class="t m5d0 x92 h35 ya2d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">accepted even in the inner circle of </div><div class="t m6a8 x92 h35 y156e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the emperor&apos;s palace. The enemy then </div><div class="t m1471 x15 h35 y7f6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">resorted to deception and cajolery </div><div class="t m11f x92 h35 y8b9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to corrupt the church. This led to the </div><div class="t mb1a x15 h35 yb9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">union of church and state. </div><div class="t m999 x71 h35 y724 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In the Middle Ages the enemy&apos;s </div><div class="t m344 x15 h35 yc3c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">purpose was accomplished through a </div><div class="t m8cb x15 h35 ye86 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">big and popular church that had </div><div class="t m1c8 x92 h35 y13ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">apostatized. The church used the </div><div class="t m66 x15 h35 y56f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">power of the law and the armies </div><div class="t mb48 x15 h35 y1795 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the state to enforce a corrupt </div><div class="t m1a4 x15 h35 y181 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">religion. This continued during most </div><div class="t ma6c x15 h35 y7b8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the dark period of the 1260 years </div><div class="t m1c8 x15 h35 y5ef ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophesied in Revelation 12:6. </div><div class="t m24c x71 h35 yfea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">At the time of the Reformation and </div><div class="t m41a x15 h35 y6d5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">afterward, near the end of that long </div><div class="t m59e x15 h35 y127e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">prophetic period, this type of action </div><div class="t m744 x15 h35 y54c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on the part of the official church was </div><div class="t m58d x15 h35 y708 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">abandoned. Today it presents a </div><div class="t m485 x15 h35 yf72 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">different front. It has even advocated </div><div class="t mac9 x15 h35 yb22 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the concept of religious liberty at </div><div class="t m554 x15 h35 y868 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Vatican Council II. For this we should </div><div class="t m588 x15 h35 y731 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">be grateful. But the inspired pen </div><div class="t m146 x15 h35 y86c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">warns us to beware of the facade; </div><div class="t m5db x15 h35 y4f4 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the real nature of apostasy has not </div><div class="t m353 x27 h35 y125a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">changed. </div><div class="t m11b x71 h35 y1548 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The old methods of persecution—</div><div class="t m727 x15 h35 y914 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">torture and death—will be resurrected </div><div class="t m247 x15 h35 y5ae ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">at the last stage of the age-long </div><div class="t m2e8 x27 h35 y8de ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">conflict between truth and error. This  </div><div class="t m2f2 x70 h35 y237f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">time, though, it will be shorter, and </div><div class="t mdfd x70 h35 y2341 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">martyrdom of believers will cease at </div><div class="t m8fd x70 h35 y2053 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the close of probation. </div><div class="t m119 x8 h35 y761 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The state, apostate churches, and </div><div class="t m54d x56 h35 y8cf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">spiritualism will unite their efforts to </div><div class="t me7b x56 h35 yed9 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">win the loyalty of millions of people. </div><div class="t me1f x8 h35 y11d6 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">During all the times of crisis in the </div><div class="t m2cc x56 h35 y7ea ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">past God has had His loyal people. In </div><div class="t m70b x56 h35 y4dc ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the last moments of human history He </div><div class="t m169 x56 h35 y50f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will continue to have His faithful </div><div class="t m3b1 x56 h35 y1699 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ones; those who keep the </div><div class="t m5f3 x56 h35 y4c1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">commandments of God and have the </div><div class="t m7b0 x56 h35 yb0b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">testimony of Jesus. They will defy </div><div class="t m5e6 x56 h35 y99f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the efforts of the persecuting powers </div><div class="t m1d1 x56 h35 y660 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and remain loyal to God. </div><div class="t m17a x78 h35 y4aa ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">In this lesson we will try to identify </div><div class="t m96c x56 h35 yb0e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the different powers that will oppose </div><div class="t mc3 x56 h35 y77c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">God&apos;s people: the dragon, the first </div><div class="t m2b6 x56 h35 y700 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">beast, the second (or lamblike) beast, </div><div class="t me19 x56 h35 y891 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the false prophet. We will see all of </div><div class="t maa8 x56 h35 y249 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">them united in a concerted and final </div><div class="t m7ed x56 h35 y4e5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">action. But God&apos;s </div><div class="t m5b2 xb6 h49 y4e5 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">people </div><div class="t m71d xea h35 y4e5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will be a </div><div class="t m1646 x56 h35 y266 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">part of the triumph of Christ, His </div><div class="t m6af x56 h35 y56d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">truth, His church, and with her, every </div><div class="t m9e8 x56 h35 y1a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">loyal one. </div><div class="t m70e x78 h35 yf6f ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">To know in advance how the great </div><div class="t mbba x56 h35 ye2 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">enemy will work through human </div><div class="t m787 x56 h35 y547 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">agencies will help us to be aware of </div><div class="t m94 x56 h35 y137d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the dangers of these final days. It </div><div class="t m1bb x7 h35 ybf1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should cause us to seek victory </div><div class="t m9b1 x56 h35 y1014 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">through the one unequaled and </div><div class="t m8ba x7 h35 y529 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">infallible source, Jesus Christ. </div><div class="t m38c x7 h49 yb1e ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m12c x7 h49 y72f ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m1372 x9f h49 y2ed ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Dragon </div><div class="t mea3 x9f h49 y709 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 12:9) </div><div class="t m814 x7 h49 ya07 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m1e5 x9f h49 y3c2 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The First Beast of Revelation 13 </div><div class="t m53c x9f h49 y1258 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 13:1) </div><div class="t m66d x7 h49 y5f1 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m1085 x9f h49 y5f1 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Second Beast of Revelation 13 </div><div class="t md0d x9f h49 y812 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 13:11-18) </div><div class="t m7e1 x7 h49 y805 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m393 x9f h49 y733 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Mark of the Beast </div><div class="t m1138 x9f h49 y122c ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 13:16, 17) </div><div class="t m2ef x7 h49 y481 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m1080 x9f h49 y533 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Triple Union </div><div class="t m31a x9f h49 y1021 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rev. 16:13) </div><div class="t mb27 x7 h49 y198e ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m674 x9f h49 y198e ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Triumphant Child of God </div><div class="t me0d x9f h49 yfd9 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(2 Cor. 11:24-27) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
